    "For each i ∈ M, the MLP maps a noisy sample-conditioned on zL i -into a denoised latent prediction ẑL i.",
    "The loss is computed only over the masked positions M.",
    "At inference, tokenwise autoregression proceeds over S autoregressive steps to predict ẐL.",
    "At step s = 0, ẐL,0 is initialized with the mask embedding, i.e.",
    "} of the masked positions (not previously selected if s > 0) are selected for generation."
